avid Shin"}],"duration":2835.5,"recordingDate":"2019-07-06T11:45:00.000Z","audioFiles":[{"url":"https://www.audioverse.org/english/download/dl/69269/2019/08/20308/20190706-1145-20308-69156d1953fde26917d03ef6ddfa3800-96k.mp3"},{"url":"https://www.audioverse.org/english/download/dl/69270/2019/08/20308/20190706-1145-20308-69156d1953fde26917d03ef6ddfa3800-48k.mp3"},{"url":"https://www.audioverse.org/english/download/dl/69271/2019/08/20308/20190706-1145-20308-69156d1953fde26917d03ef6ddfa3800-16k.mp3"}],"description":"<p>Pastor David shares an apologetic presentation defending the sanctuary message from its detractors such as Ford and Brimsmead. Listen to this presentation to be more firmly established on the veracity of the sanctuary message.</p>"},{"id":"20614","title":"Take It Home","imageWithFallback":{"url":"https://s.audioverse.org/english/gallery/sponsors/_/50/50/restoration_international.jpg"},"persons":[{"name":"Alane Waters"},{"name":"Tom Waters"}],"duration":3186,"recordingDate":"2019-09-30T12:36:00.000Z","audioFiles":[{"url":"https://www.audioverse.org/english/download/dl/70567/2019/09/20614/20190930-1236-20614-a23dbd888166c7c317f8dc47f37c08b8-96k.mp3"},{"url":"https://www.audioverse.org/english/download/dl/70568/2019/09/20614/20190930-1236-20614-a23dbd888166c7c317f8dc47f37c08b8-48k.mp3"},{"url":"https://www.audioverse.org/english/download/dl/70569/2019/09/20614/20190930-1236-20614-a23dbd888166c7c317f8dc47f37c08b8-16k.mp3"}],"description":"<p>We're often inspired with what we hear, but are we ready to take it home with us and be different people willing to walk in His steps.</p>"}]}},"staticQueryHashes":["3649515864"]}